OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright and
OL,6,Fsunny end to the day. Dry with thin
OL,7,Fhigh cloud overnight but staying dry
OL,8,Fwith light wind. Another warm night
OL,9,Ffor many, especially in urban areas
OL,10,Fand cities, while feeling cooler
OL,11,Facross coastal parts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FAnother hot day, with daytime
OL,14,Ftemperatures widely above average. Dry
OL,15,Fand predominantly clear with hazy
OL,16,Fsunshine in the morning. Cooler along
OL,17,Fcoastal areas, with an onshore breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
