OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FEarly
OL,6,Fmorning low cloud quickly burning
OL,7,Fback, turning sunny by the afternoon
OL,8,Fon both Saturday and Sunday. Dry with
OL,9,Fplenty of sunshine on Monday, coastal
OL,10,Flow cloud may return later.
